Get free icons in iOS 16 Filled design style

Our consistent iOS Filled icon pack covers diverse theme categories and follows the guidelines from Apple.

  • These icons are pixel-perfect at 50×50 pixels.
  • The style is outlined with a base stroke of 2px.
  • All the icons have an outline iOS icon version. This pack works for iOS applications with vertical lists, like iOS Mail App.

The Icons8 team created all the icons in-house, started immediately after the iOS 7 release, and drawing it up to this day.

Download free iOS Filled icons in different themes for your UI needs. The graphics are available in both PNG and vector.
